8:
The Lord has warned the descendants of Jacob;
\q2 he has said that he will punish Israel.
\q1

14:
Therefore, in one day Yahweh will get rid of those who are like Israel's head and those who are like its tail;
\q2 the ones who are like the top of the palm tree and the ones who are like the bottom.
\q1

16:
The leaders of the people have misled them;
\q2 they have caused the people that they are ruling to be confused.
\q1
